        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued September 8 at 4:50PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 450 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 9
miles west of Conlen, or 11 miles northeast of Dalhart, moving
southeast at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Dalhart.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
